ing%20a%20brief%20visit%20with%20him%20when%20he%20was%20around%205.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20go%20on.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb12381b-3f22-4dc8-8ceb-8221d344307c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20turned%20to%20my%20computer%20for%20answers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20some%20answers%20and%20fill%20out%20at%20least%20part%20of%20the%20family%20tree%20for%20my%20dad's%20side%20of%20the%20family%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20have%20to%20fend%20for%20myself.%20I%20decided%20to%20use%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FAncestry.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Ancestry.com%20to%20help%3C%2Fa%3E%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20put%20my%20grandfather's%20name%20in%20Ancestry.%20I%20used%20his%20obituary%20as%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20his%20birth%20and%20death%2C%20his%20parents'%20names%2C%20and%20his%20brother's%20name%2C%20then%20I%20searched%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ancestry-uses-ai-records-processing-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecensus%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20birth%20and%20marriage%20certificates%2C%20military%20records%2C%20and%20more.%20I%20began%20slowly%20gathering%20documents%20from%20his%20life%20that%20could%20help%20me%20build%20a%20family%20tree%20for%20my%20father's%20side%20of%20the%20family.%20Soon%2C%20his%20profile%20showed%20leaf%20icons%2C%20which%20the%20site%20uses%20as%20%26quot%3Bhints%26quot%3B%20for%20me%20to%20explore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Census%20records%20the%20author%20researched%20to%20find%20more%20clue%20about%20her%20family%20history.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6957d70c64858d02d217a6eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221278%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECensus%20records%20the%20author%20researched%20to%20find%20more%20clue%20about%20her%20family%20history.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Isobella%20Jade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3