0and%20Jay%20Kaplan%2C%20an%20internal%20portfolio%20manager%20focused%20on%20IPOs.%20Singh%20said%20Paloma%20is%20%26quot%3Bagnostic%26quot%3B%20about%20whether%20portfolio%20managers%20would%20run%20money%20internally%20on%20Paloma's%20platform%20or%20externally%20at%20their%20own%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20competing%20against%20everyone%26quot%3B%20for%20talent%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20and%20Paloma%20has%20plans%20to%20get%20bigger%20in%20every%20facet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2297f35b33-d659-4185-b858-84debeee5ceb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20on%20Paloma's%20reputation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20firm's%20recent%20turbulence%2C%20the%20Paloma%20name%20still%20carries%20weight%20in%20the%20quant%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20heard%20legendary%20stories%20about%20Paloma%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20JB%20Kim%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20quant%20fund%20nVerses%2C%20which%20manages%20capital%20from%20the%20firm.%20A%20backer%20of%20D.E.%20Shaw%2C%20Nassim%20Taleb's%20now-shuttered%20Empirica%20Capital%2C%20and%20LMR%2C%20Sussman%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20held%20in%20high%20esteem%20among%20the%20systematic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Singh%20and%20DeAddio%20want%20talented%20PMs%20in%20other%20asset%20classes%20as%20well.%20The%20multistrategy%20fund%20aims%20to%20be%20split%20equally%20between%20fundamental%20stockpickers%2C%20systematic%20traders%2C%20and%20credit%20funds%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20and%20the%20manager%20has%20also%20added%20a%20few%20volatility%20traders%20to%20diversify%20the%20return%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20firm's%20best%20bets%20in%20recent%20years%20is%20London-based%20credit%20fund%20Sona%20Asset%20Management%2C%20which%20has%20surged%20to%20more%20than%20%2415%20billion%20in%20assets%20after%20originally%20launching%20with%20an%20SMA%20from%20Paloma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Sussman%20stands%20behind%20a%20podium%20in%20a%20suit%20and%20tie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6953e1fc04eda4732f2e3df0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBillionaire%20Donald%20Sussman%20founded%20Paloma%20more%20than%2040%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3EPaloma%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma's%20top%20three%20executives%2C%20along%20with%20Sussman%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20chairman%2C%20make%20up%20the%20office%20of%20the%20CIO%2C%20and%20they've%20defined%20the%20type%20of%20investor%20they're%20looking%20for%20as%20%26quot%3Bestablished%20emerging%20managers.%26quot%3B%20Strategies%20that%20require%20years%20of%20work%20before%20they%20can%20begin%20trading%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20are%20not%20wanted%2C%20but%20the%20firm%20is%20willing%20to%20be%20more%20flexible%20on%20risk%20than%20others%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20model%20has%20supported%20a%20strong%20track%20record%20of%20successful%20launches%20and%20reinforced%20our%20reputation%20as%20a%20founder-friendly%20capital%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investors%20they're%20seeking%20are%20tired%20of%20one-size-fits-all%20platforms%20and%20often%20run%20more%20constrained%20strategies.%20Both%20internal%20PMs%20and%20external%20fund%20managers%20own%20their%20intellectual%20property%20and%20track%20record%2C%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf75b647-36a4-4db6-b63d-33c97d85665f%5C%22%3E'High-touch'%20talent%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%245%20trillion%20hedge%20fund%20industry%20deals%20with%20an%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-pay-poaching-relocation-mercenaries-buy-loyalty-millennium-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalent%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%20the%20model%20the%20firm%20has%20used%20to%20recruit%20and%20retain%20talented%20investors%20is%20%26quot%3Bhigh-touch.%26quot%3B%20Paloma%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20likely%20never%20grow%20to%20be%20hundreds%20of%20investing%20teams%20like%20Millennium%20or%20Citadel%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firm%20doubled%20its%20investor%20head%20count%20in%202025%20to%20roughly%2025%20portfolio%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20but%20can%20continue%20to%20add%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20investors%20for%20their%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20PMs%20are%20likely%20more%20tenured%20in%20their%20careers%20and%20not%20looking%20to%20jump%20to%20whichever%20fund%20is%20offering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-hedge-fund-managers-are-paid-move-firms-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20highest%20guaranteed%20payou%3C%2Fa%3Et%20at%20the%20time.%20Singh%20said%20the%20firm%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20costs%20and%20avoiding%20bidding%20wars%20for%20PMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh-touch%26quot%3B%20model%20is%20defined%20by%20a%20close%20working%20relationship%20with%20Singh%2C%20DeAddio%2C%20and%20the%20firm's%20chief%20risk%20officer%2C%20Grant%20Rippetoe%2C%20that%20can%20be%20more%20customized%20to%20the%20individual%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20nVerses%2C%20who%20started%20his%20firm%20in%202021%20with%20capital%20from%20Millennium%20before%20Izzy%20Englander's%20firm%20redeemed%20its%20money%2C%20said%20he%20communicates%20with%20DeAddio%20every%20day%20and%20was%20able%20to%20start%20trading%20four%20months%20after%20getting%20Paloma's%20capital%2C%20a%20remarkably%20fast%20timeframe%20for%20a%20systematic%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fad927b-c011-413b-928a-e1f512466248%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReady%20to%20grow%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20big%20the%20firm%20grows%20its%20asset%20base%20is%20still%20undetermined.%20What%20is%20known%20is%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20firm's%20current%20roster%20of%20investors%20to%20handle%20more%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20talent%20pip