20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshapes-pitch-deck-funding-hr-ai-agents-dreamteam-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eagent-based%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20rapid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20SaaStr%20had%20just%20one%20AI%20agent%20in%20production%20that%20it%20used%20for%20various%20digital%20tasks%2C%20Lemkin%20said.%20That%20month%2C%20though%2C%20during%20the%20SaaStr%20Annual%20%E2%80%94%20its%20yearly%20gathering%20of%20over%2010%2C000%20founders%2C%20executives%2C%20and%20VCs%20%E2%80%94%20two%20of%20its%20high-paid%20sales%20representatives%20abruptly%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemkin%20said%20he%20turned%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-chief-ai-officer-general-motors-describes-role-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echief%20AI%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20done%20with%20hiring%20humans%20in%20sales.%20We're%20going%20to%20push%20the%20limits%20with%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemkin's%20calculus%20was%20that%20it%20just%20wasn't%20worth%20the%20cost%20of%20hiring%20another%20junior%20sales%20representative%20for%20a%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year%20position%20who%20would%20eventually%20quit%2C%20when%20he%20could%20use%20a%20loyal%20AI%20agent%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmelia%20Lerutte%2C%20SaaStr's%20chief%20AI%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20by%20email%20that%20by%20June%2C%20the%20company%20began%20ramping%20up%20the%20number%20of%20agents%20it%20had%20in%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20only%201%20non-core%20agent%20at%20the%20time%20with%20Delphi%2C%20but%20didn't%20go%20deep%20on%202%20to%2020%2B%20until%20the%20beginning%20of%20June%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20conscious%20choice%20after%20their%20departure%20to%20reallocate%20some%20(but%20not%20all)%20head%20count%20spend%20to%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20SaaStr%20office%2C%20the%2010%20desks%20that%20once%20belonged%20to%20humans%20on%20the%20go-to-market%20team%20are%20now%20labeled%20with%20the%20names%20of%20agents%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BQuali%20for%20qualified%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BArty%20for%20artisan%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BRepli%20for%20Replit%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemkin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemkin%20said%20SaaStr%20is%20training%20its%20agents%20on%20its%20best%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrain%20an%20agent%20with%20your%20best%20person%2C%20and%20best%20script%2C%20then%20that%20agent%20can%20start%20to%20become%20a%20version%20of%20your%20best%20salesperson%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaaStr's%20process%20is%20similar%20to%20how%20Vercel%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agent-entry-level-sales-jobs-vercel-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud-based%20platform%20for%20developers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trained%20a%20sales%20agent%20off%20its%20top%20performer%20for%20six%20weeks%20by%20documenting%20every%20step%20of%20their%20work%2C%20and%20then%20building%20an%20agent%20to%20mimic%20their%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20are%20experimenting%20with%20AI%20agents%2C%20but%20risks%20remain.%20One%20of%20the%20big%20ones%20is%20the%20threat%20of%20data%20leaks%20and%20cybercrime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20agents%2C%20in%20order%20to%20have%20their%20full%20functionality%2C%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20access%20applications%2C%20often%20need%20to%20access%20the%20operating%20system%20or%20the%20OS%20level%20of%20the%20device%20on%20which%20you're%20running%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Harry%20Farmer%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20at%20the%20Ada%20Lovelace%20Institute%2C%20recently%20told%20Wired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20access%20creates%20more%20potential%20attack%20points%20for%20cybercriminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20threats%20aside%2C%20Lemkin%20said%20that%20the%20net%20productivity%20of%20agents%20is%20about%20the%20same%20as%20humans.%20However%2C%