ecruiting%20pressure%20fueled%20a%20culture%20of%20fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20marine%20recruiter%20in%20a%20neighborhood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69542b1604eda4732f2e4618%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Rota%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiting%20new%20Marines%20can%20be%20so%20challenging%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20US%20that%20some%20recruiters%20have%20resorted%20to%20fraud%20to%20meet%20their%20monthly%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20obtained%20a%202023%20Marine%20Corps%20investigation%20into%20one%20area%20of%20the%20Rust%20Belt%20that%20found%20widespread%20rule-breaking%2C%20including%20fabricated%20police%20records%20and%20fake%20medical%20notes.%20Two%20recruiters%20who%20were%20fired%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20the%20pressures%20of%20recruiting%20and%20what%20drove%20them%20to%20fake%20records.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Staff%20Sgt.%20Calvin%20Grimes%2C%20shared%20a%20collection%20of%20electronic%20templates%20that%20helped%20fellow%20recruiters%20forge%20doctors'%20notes%2C%20high%20school%20diplomas%2C%20and%20other%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20live%20with%20that%20feeling%20that%20your%20heart's%20beating%20out%20of%20your%20chest%20ready%20to%20explode%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Gunnery%20Sgt.%20Logan%20Krivak%20said%20of%20falsifying%20records.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20it's%20wrong%2C%20and%20you%20just%20have%20to%20live%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%2010%20Marines%20who%20recruited%20in%20the%20region%20between%202018%20and%202024%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20faced%20a%20desperate%20struggle%20to%20hit%20their%20quotas%20of%20signing%20up%20two%20new%20recruits%20each%20month.%20Five%20admitted%20to%20taking%20shortcuts%20or%20falsifying%20records.%20The%20others%20said%20they%20knew%20fraud%20was%20happening%20within%20recruiting%20ranks.%20In%202021%2C%20all%20the%20leaders%20in%20one%20recruiting%20hub%20were%20relieved%20for%20fraud%2C%20or%20for%20failing%20to%20catch%20it%2C%20sources%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rust%20Belt%20issues%20spotlight%20a%20problem%20that%20persists%20in%20some%20areas%20today%2C%20recruiters%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20Marines%20with%20Marine%20Corps%20Recruiting%20and%20Retention%20School.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6945845464858d02d21726a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20recruiters%20in%20the%20Rust%20Belt%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20pressure%20to%20succeed%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20well-qualified%20young%20people%20drove%20them%20to%20break%20rules.%20Roughly%2075%25%20of%20American%20youth%20cannot%20meet%20the%20military's%20fitness%20or%20academic%20requirements%20to%20enlist.%3Cp%3EDefense%20Visual%20Information%20Distribution%20Service%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFraudulent%20enlistment%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bfraud%2C%26quot%3B%20involves%20false%20claims%20in%20the%20recruiting%20process%20by%20a%20recruit%20or%20recruiter.%20It%20can%20include%20hiding%20the%20truth%2C%20forging%20a%20missing%20signature%2C%20fabricating%20official%20documents%2C%20or%20bypassing%20waivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20shortcuts%20can%20help%20recruiters%20avoid%20delays%20that%20could%20stop%20them%20from%20meeting%20their%20goals.%20But%20they%20carry%20risks%3A%20They%20can%20derail%20a%20recruit's%20career%20or%20jeopardize%20their%20health%2C%20and%20for%20recruiters%2C%20falsifying%20records%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20military%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20weighs%20on%20anybody%20who%20has%20a%20conscience%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20current%20recruiter%20working%20in%20the%20Northeast%20said%20of%20such%20rule-breaking.%20%26quot%3BYou%20start%20walking%20that%20line%20into%20that%20gray%20area%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20your%20hard%20line%20is%20in%20the%20sand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c4795fa-6c5e-4a41-88ff-07c891c6be25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20forged%20police%20document%20kicks%20off%20an%20investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20investigation%2C%20being%20revealed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20focused%20on%20the%204th%20Marine%20Corps%20District%2C%20which%20covers%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregions-america-bible-belt-rust-belt-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERust%20Belt%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20parts%20of%20Appalachia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tough%20region%20for%20recruiters%20to%20meet%20their%20monthly%20goal%3B%20then%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20making%20it%20even%20more%20of%20a%20challenge%2C%20said%20Krivak%2C%20who%20recruited%20in%20the%20region%20from%202015%20to%202018%20and%20returned%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20first%20stint%20was%20brutal%20but%20survivable.%20He%20recalled%20regularly%20meeting%20his%20quotas%2C%20at%20times%20even%20exceeding%20them.%20Krivak%20said%20he%20never%20engaged%20in%20fraud%20on%20his%20first%20tour%20%E2%80%94%20his%20superiors%20rigorously%20condemned%20it.%20When%20he%20returned%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20motivated%20by%20the%20stability%20the%20job%20could%20provide%2C%20things%20had%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20Business%20Insider%20investigation%20into%20Marine%20recruiter%20welfare.%20Read%20the%20first%20installment%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarines-recruiting-crisis-enlistment-quotas-burnout-mental-health-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20hidden%20Marine%20Corps%20recruiting%20crisis%20that's%20'burning%20Marines'%20to%20fill%20the%20ranks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20tuned%20for%20parts%20three%20and%20four%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E'Burden%20of%20command'%3A%20How%20a%20brutal%20recruiting%20mission%20broke%20some%20Marines%20leading%20the%20charge%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20military%20is%20running%20out%20of%20teenagers%20to%20recruit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20old-school%20methods%20to%20reach%20them%20are%20failing%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fresh%20source%20of%20stress%20was%20Military%20Health%20System%20Genesis%2C%20a%20newly%20rolled-out%20medical%20data%20system%20that%20flagged%20potential%20recruits'%20medical%20histories.%20The%20system%20halted%20processing%20for%20applicants%20with%20issues%20that%20could%20make%20service%20dangerous%2C%20such%20as%20asthma%20or%20heart%20problems.%20It%20also%20flagged%20seemingly%20minor%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20surgical%20scars%20or%20broken%20bones%20from%20a%20decade%20earlier%2C%20which%20tangled%20recruiters%20in%20a%20web%20of%20administrative%20roadblocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20crunch%20to%20hit%20monthly%20recruiting%20quotas%2C%20recruiters%20like%20Krivak%20felt%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20wait%20weeks%20for%20medical%20waivers%20that%20would%20override%20the%20Genesis%20flags.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECOVID%20had%20already%20restricted%20access%20to%20high%20schools%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estraining%20relationships%20with%20teachers%20and%20students%2C%20and%20making%20recruiting%20even%20more%20difficult.%20Krivak's%20territory%20proved%20dismal%20hunting%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20solid%20candidates%20could%20present%20unexpected%20challenges%2C%20Krivak%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20said%2C%20in%20areas%20riddled%20with%20drug%20problems%2C%20recruiters%20could%20struggle%20to%20get%20a%20teen's%20non-sober%20parent%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20enlistment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20being%20asked%20for%20a%20police%20document%20in%202022%20to%20verify%20that%20an%20applicant's%20tattoos%20weren't%20gang-related.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20given%20several%20hours%20to%20obtain%20the%20document%2C%20and%20that%20the%20short%20timeline%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20fake%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20asking%20you%20to%20do%20this%20the%20right%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrivak%20forged%20the%20document%2C%20he%20said%2C%20arousing%20suspicion%20at%20a%20higher%20level%20upon%20inspection%2C%20the%20investigation%20found.%20Later%20relieved%20of%20duty%20and%20punished%20for%20the%20forgery%2C%20he%20ultimately%20left%20the%20Marine%20Corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229f49c9a-7a64-4fdd-b067-2fc0eab900bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWidespread%20rule-breaking%20is%20uncovered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKrivak's%20forged%20document%20helped%20kick%20off%20a%20deeper%20examination%20into%20fellow%20recruiters%2C%20including%20Grimes%2C%20who%20maintained%20the%20electronic%20templates%20for%20falsifying%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20templates%2C%20which%20were%20referenced%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20could%20be%20modified%20to%20create%20false%20hearing%20test%20results%2C%20high%20school%20diplomas%2C%20or%20doctors'%20notes%20clearing%20applicants%20of%20old%20medical%20issues.%20Grimes%20shared%20the%20templates%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20for%20the%202023%20investigation%2C%20Grimes%20said%20that%20he%20had%20been%20tacitly%20encouraged%20to%20engage%20in%20such%20deceit%20from%20his%20very%20first%20month%20on%20the%20job.%20He%20said%20a%20supervising%20recruiter%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20do%20what%20you%20have%20to%20do%20to%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Grimes%2C%20who%20was%20also%20relieved%20of%20duty%2C%20fraudulent%20activity%20had%20become%20the%20norm%2C%20a%20response%20to%20what%20he%20and%20others%20described%20as%20dismal%20recruiting%20conditions%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20pandemic.%20Fraud%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20a%20way%20to%20process%20applicants%20faster%20and%20give%20exhausted%20and%20overworked%20subordinates%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalk%20to%20Grimes%2C%26quot%3B%20some%20fellow%20recruiters%20would%20say%20when%20a%20tricky%20case%20needed%20help%2C%20Grimes%20and%20others%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Grimes%20and%20Krivak%20now%20work%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d9b8ff1-5649-457e-9fc5-f0db1f28b1db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20Corps%20addresses%20fraud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFraud%20isn't%20ubiquitous%20across%20the%20Corps%2C%20recruiters%20said%3B%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20concentrated%20in%20areas%20where%20recruiting%20pressures%20are%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20current%20and%20former%20recruiters%20outside%20the%20Rust%20Belt%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20had%20never%20witnessed%20fraud.%20Others%20said%20fraud%20has%20always%20existed%2C%20though%20only%20in%20small%20circles.%20All%20condemned%20it%20and%20agreed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20fraud%20involved%20shortcuts%20that%20didn't%20jeopardize%20health%20or%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFraud%20only%20works%20with%20a%20level%20of%20plausible%20deniability%2C%20recruiters%20said%2C%20and%20must%20be%20tightly%20guarded.%20When%20others%20outside%20the%20circle%2C%20especially%20officers%2C%20get%20wind%20of%20it%2C%20things%20can%20unravel%20quickly.%20The%20Corps%20is%20swift%20to%20punish%20those%20who%20are%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Marine%20Corps%20recruiter%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20an%20inflatable%20Marine%20Corps%20drill%20instructor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694584e504eda4732f2ddfe0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22949%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20the%20Army%20and%20Navy%20fell%20short%20of%20their%20recruiting%20goals%20by%20thousands%20of%20recruits%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20always%20met%20its%20goals.%3Cp%3EDefense%20Visual%20Information%20Distribution%20Service%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20fraud%2C%20like%20a%20fudged%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esignature%20or%20a%20fabricated%20diploma%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20harm%20an%20applicant's%20health.%20Rarer%2C%20more%20serious%20examples%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Grimes%20confessed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20to%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erisked%20putting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-wants-to-prevent-muscle-breakdowns-with-new-playbook-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecruit's%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20jeopardy%2C%20such%20as%20fake%20lung%20or%20heart%20health%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20committing%20fraud%20left%20them%20with%20guilt%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20regret.%20Some%20described%20becoming%20numb%20to%20it%2C%20saying%20that%20shipping%20fraud-tinged%20applicants%20to%20boot%20camp%20earned%20them%20a%20pat%20on%20the%20back%20for%20helping%20their%20unit%20reach%20its%20goals.%20Other%20Marines%20who%20refused%20to%20engage%20in%20fraud%20said%20they%20struggled%2C%20facing%20pressure%20to%20succeed%20when%20others%20seemed%20to%20be%20cheating%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20reporting%20on%20how%20recruiting%20practices%20and%20policies%20are%20evolving%20across%20the%20US%20military.%20If%20you%20have%20insight%20into%20current%20challenges%2C%20emerging%20trends%2C%20or%20future-focused%20initiatives%2C%20we'd%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Reach%20this%20reporter%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20kelseybaker75.75%20or%20by%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akbaker%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekbaker%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EGrimes%20and%20Krivak%20said%20they%20struggled%20to%20reconcile%20their%20punishment%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20their%20supervising%20officer%20knowingly%20allowed%20fraud%20to%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20though%20the%20investigation%20disputes%20these%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20cultural%20acceptance%20in%20some%20areas%20that%20is%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20the%20Marine%20for%20the%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fraud%2C%20said%20a%20former%20recruiting%20supervisor%20who%20remains%20on%20active%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Marine%20Corps%20Recruiting%20Command%20spokesman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bindependent%20quality%20control%26quot%3B%20checks%20throughout%20the%20enlistment%20process%20serve%20as%20guardrails%20to%20help%20mitigate%20fraud%2C%20along%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Brigorous%26quot%3B%20records%20review%20for%20recruits%20upon%20arrival%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarine-corps-boot-camp-crucible-recruits-parris-island-gender-integrated-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboot%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Marine%20Corps%20does%20not%20condone%20or%20allow%20fraud%20by%20Marines%20or%20by%20applicants%20seeking%20to%20enter%20the%20Marine%20Corps%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20service%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20violate%20ethical%20regulations%20or%20law%20are%20held%20to%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20things%20have%20improved%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20insiders%20said%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20to%20alleviate%20pressure%20on%20recruiters.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20MCRC%20underwent%20an%20overhaul%2C%20opening%20more%20hubs%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BSouthern%20Smile%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20Florida%20and%20Texas%2C%20w