e%20emails%20show%20how%20Cuban%20responds%20to%20startup%20founders%2C%20assesses%20business%20pitches%2C%20and%20decides%20to%20invest%20over%20email%2C%20as%20the%20billionaire%20has%20said%20he's%20done%20many%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20put%20a%20potential%20seed%20opportunity%20that%20I%20think%20might%20be%20a%20strong%20mutual%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20wrote%20in%20his%20initial%20message%20to%20Cuban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Clipbook%20founder%20then%20provided%20a%20bullet-point%20summary%20of%20his%20startup%2C%20which%20uses%20AI%20to%20track%20how%20people%20and%20companies%20are%20being%20discussed%20online%2C%20like%20a%20more%20sophisticated%20version%20of%20Google%20Alerts.%20Joseph%20worked%20in%20PR%20for%20a%20few%20years%20and%20said%20he%20felt%20the%20%26quot%3Bpain%20points%26quot%3B%20of%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20public%20sentiment%2C%20which%20he%20thought%20AI%20could%20help%20solve.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-new-ai-chatbot-conversation-with-questions-answers-examples-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhen%20ChatGPT%20launched%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%202022%2C%20Joseph%20said%20it%20became%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20obvious%26quot%3B%20that%20AI%20could%20transform%20PR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Joseph's%20pitch%20right%20away.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20entrepreneur%20followed%20up%2C%20adding%20that%20he's%20backed%20by%20Dan%20Pfeiffer%2C%20co-host%20of%20the%20popular%20politics%20show%20%26quot%3BPod%20Save%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20day%2C%20Cuban%20responded.%20He%20requested%20a%20sample%20report%20for%20his%20own%20name%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20tech%20in%20action.%20He%20also%20asked%20how%20Clipbook%20differed%20from%20Google%20Alerts%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20what%20the%20founder%20was%20seeking%20from%20him%20%E2%80%94%20and%20under%20what%20terms.%20From%20there%2C%20Joseph%20and%20Cuban%20traded%20a%20few%20more%20emails%20and%20hopped%20on%20a%20call.%20Soon%20after%2C%20they%20reached%20a%20deal%2C%20Joseph%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20moved%20more%20aggressively%20and%20faster%20with%20Mark%20than%20I%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20later%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20said%20Cuban%20vetted%20him%2C%20not%20just%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20just%20really%20doing%20a%20360%2C%20just%20pressure-testing%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20more%20importantly%2C%20probably%2C%20pressure-testing%20me%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%20So%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20come%20in%20pretty%20hot%20with%20some%20pretty%20aggressive%20questions%20I%20think%20was%20also%20really%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20really%2C%20actually%2C%20in%20retrospect%2C%20a%20really%20positive%20signal%20that%20he%20was%20very%20interested%20in%20the%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20email%20exchanges%20between%20Joseph%20and%20Cuban%2C%20which%20Joseph%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20Cuban%20gave%20Business%20Insider%20permission%20to%20publish%20their%20content.%20The%20original%20text%20and%20formatting%20have%20been%20preserved%2C%20with%20small%20modifications%20for%20clarity.%20Certain%20sensitive%20information%2C%20like%20email%20addresses%20and%20Clipbook's%20revenue%2C%20has%20been%20redacted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EAdam%20Joseph%20to%20Mark%20Cuban%20%E2%80%94%2012%2F28%2F2024%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESubject%3A%20Clipbook%20seed%20opportunity%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EHello%20Mr.%20Cuban%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20name%20is%20Adam%20Joseph%20and%20I'm%20the%20CEO%20of%20Clipbook.%20I%20wanted%20to%20put%20a%20potential%20seed%2B%20opportunity%20that%20I%20think%20might%20be%20a%20strong%20mutual%20fit.%