0that%20Dan%20Pfeiffer%20-%20former%20White%20House%20Communications%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20chief%20strategist%20under%20President%20Obama%20(and%20top%2010%20charts%20podcaster%20of%20Pod%20Save%20America)%20is%20also%20an%20investor.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3ECuban%20to%20Joseph%20%E2%80%94%2012%2F29%2F2024%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ECan%20you%20send%20me%20a%20sample%20on%20my%20name%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20content%20aggregators%20that%20distribute%20via%20email%2C%20including%20Google%20alerts.%20Why%20couldn't%20they%20do%20the%20same%20%3F%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhat%20are%20youooking%20%3Cem%3E%5Bsic%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20from%20me%20and%20what%20do%20I%20get%20for%20it%20%3F%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EJoseph%20to%20Cuban%20%E2%80%94%2012%2F29%2F2024%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThanks%20so%20much%20for%20your%20response!%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ECircling%20soon%20with%20an%20example%20for%20you.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20like%20to%20chat%20live%3F%20I'm%20at%20%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Call%20anytime%20and%20I'll%20answer.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETo%20answer%20your%20questions%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EContent%20sources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20signed%20agreements%20with%20%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20don't%20have%20exclusives%20yet%20but%20overall%20don't%20think%20it%20is%20a%20must-have%20to%20get%20us%20to%20100M%20in%20ARR%20%3Cem%3E%5Bannual%20recurring%20revenue%5D%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHappy%20to%20discuss%20but%20will%20mention%20that%20the%20largest%20legacy%20player%2C%20%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20no%20longer%20has%20exclusivity%20with%20any%20major%20media%20provider%20as%20of%20this%20year.%20(They%20used%20to%20have%20Dow%20Jones%20%2F%20WSJ.)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20Alerts%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Simply%20put%20-%20Google%20Alerts%20is%20a%20consumer-level%20tool%20that%20does%20not%20meet%20the%20enterprise%20needs%20of%20a%20large%20business.%20It's%20why%20this%20segment%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20Alerts%20might%20be%20fine%20to%20track%2C%20say%2C%20track%20a%20simple%20name%20or%20org.%20But%20the%20100B%20of%20spending%20of%20knowledge%20workers%20doing%20this%20has%20more%20nuanced%20needs%20for%20complex%20enterprises.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3EFor%20example%20(real%20example%20from%20our%20client)%3A%20say%20you%20are%20the%20Center%20for%20Audit%20Quality%20-%20the%20lobby%20%2F%20advocacy%20group%20for%20the%20large%20audit%20firms%20(Big%204%2C%20e.g.%20Deloitte%2C%20PWC%2C%20etc).%20You%20are%20actively%20tracking%20really%20important%20topics%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBig%204%20news%20as%20they%20pertains%20%3Cem%3E%5Bsic%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20big%20strategic%20initiatives%20around%20the%20audit%20business%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESalients%20%3Cem%3E%5Bsic%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20industry%20groups%20%26amp%3B%20stakeholders%20-%20but%20only%20if%20the%20%3Cem%3E%5Bsic%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3Enews%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPolicy%20announcements%20related%20to%20finance%20%26amp%3B%20policy%20broken%20down%20by%20the%20local%2C%20state%2C%20and%20federal%20level%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20differentiators%20from%20Google%20Alerts%20%2F%20legacy%20tools%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETake%20the%20human%20out%20of%20the%20loop%20for%20the%20workflow%20-%20savings%20100s%20of%20hours%20for%20our%20users%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E1000x%20more%20precise%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20comprehensive%2C%20predictive%2C%20and%20tailored%20search%20capabilities%20using%20AI-native%20technology.%20We%20can%20also%20search%20hundreds%20of%20topics%2C%20terms%2C%20stakeholders%20in%20parallel%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20access%20other%20data%20partnerships%20to%20integrate%20impressions%20data%20from%20the%20publishers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20integrate%20data%20sources%20not%20accessible%20to%20Google%20Alerts%20(e.g.%20add%20multi-modal%20search%20to%20TV%2C%20radio%2C%20podcast%2C%20direct%20government%20data%2C%20competitor%20websites%2C%20social%20media%2C%20etc%20-%20other%20sources%20manually%20searched%20by%20these%20knowledge%20workers)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERobust%20analytics%20%26amp%3B%20flurry%20of%20other%20features%20set%20that%20add%20value%20to%20customers%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20here%20on%20Google%20Alerts%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20they%20aren't%20moving%20quickly%20%26amp%3B%20putting%20the%20time%2C%20resources%2C%20or%20innovation%20on%20the%20offering.%20It's%20not%20a%20strategic%20focus%20and%20we%20will%20move%20faster%20%26amp%3B%20more%20effectively%20than%20they%20will.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20what%20I'd%20like%20from%20you%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%5Bredacted%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpen%20to%20broad%20check%20size%20range%20here%20depending%20on%20your%20appetite%20%26amp%3B%20open%20to%20discussing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe've%20raised%20entirely%20on%20YC%20SAFEs%20so%20far%20%26amp%3B%20expediency%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3EYou%20are%20a%20very%20strong%20strategic%20fit%20for%20us%2C%20given%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThroughline%20with%20your%20past%20work%20in%20media%20%2F%20TMT%20%2F%20similar%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20value%20capital%20efficiency%20(as%20we%20clearly%20do%20having%20bootstrapped%20to%20over%201M%20in%20ARR%20initially)%20aligns%20with%20how%20we%20quickly%20scaled.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20are%20AI%20%2F%20B2B%20SaaS%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Csection%3EThanks%20much!%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBest%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAdam%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3ECuban%20to%20Joseph%20%E2%80%94%2012%2F31%2F2024%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI'm%20travelling%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days.%20Go%20ahead%20and%20send%20the%20note.%20Are%20there%20any%20investor%20protections%20or%20is%20it%20standard%20SAFE%3F%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3ECuban%20to%20Joseph%20%E2%80%94%201%2F3%2F2025%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EHappy%20to%20answer%20any%20questions%20you%20have.%20Let's%20Get%20it%20done%20!%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EM%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EJoseph%20to%20Cuban%20%E2%80%94%201%2F3%2F2025%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESounds%20good%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EProbably%20some%20execution%20lessons%20I%20can%20learn%20from%20that%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAppreciate%20you%20-%20happy%20friday%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3ECuban%20to%20Joseph%20%E2%80%94%201%2F3%2F2025%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3Elol.%20Thats%20the%20goal.%20Too%20many%20calls%20and%20meetings.%20Only%20fly%20if%20you%20are%20getting%20money%20or%20closing%20a%20deal.%20Otherwise%20zoom.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIf%20you%20can't%20convey%20in%20the%20zoom%2C%20your%20message%20isn't%20crisp%20and%20on%20target%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EM%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-investment-email-ai-startup-clipbook-founder-adam-joseph-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767606301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69541634832e0ef1ead6f533%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com