%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20version%20of%20capitalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hyper-state-led.%20Many%20governments%2C%20including%20those%20of%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20make%20direct%20investments%20in%20some%20domestic%20firms.%20The%20US%20%3Cem%3Ehas%3C%2Fem%3E%20gotten%20extra%20involved%20in%20private%20industry%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20it's%20generally%20been%20in%20times%20of%20distress%2C%20such%20as%20during%20the%202008%20crisis%2C%20when%20it%20took%20stakes%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-jpmorgan-wells-fargo-investor-adam-schwartz-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecertain%20financial%20institution%3C%2Fa%3Es%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-ford-chrysler-almost-died-during-financial-crisis-changes-since-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautomakers%20in%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prevent%20a%20broader%20economic%20meltdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20it's%20different%3A%20The%20government%20is%20meddling%20when%20there's%20no%20apparent%20urgent%20need%2C%20and%20it's%20picking%20companies%20in%20what%20some%20observers%20say%20is%20a%20scattershot%20manner.%20The%20sectors%20make%20sense%2C%20but%20the%20criteria%20for%20selecting%20companies%20are%20rather%20unclear%2C%20as%20is%20the%20role%20the%20government%20will%20play%20in%20its%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20industrial%20policy%2C%20the%20devil's%20in%20the%20details%20of%20so%20much%2C%20and%20this%20is%20where%20the%20details%20are%20really%20obscured%2C%20and%20where%20they%20are%20defined%2C%20they're%20kind%20of%20ad%20hoc%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nathan%20Lane%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20economic%20development%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20Political%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20novel%20vision%20of%20American%20state%20capitalism%20is%20emerging%20right%20before%20our%20eyes.%20It's%20a%20world%20where%20the%20White%20House%20puts%20its%20thumb%20on%20the%20scale%2C%20whether%20in%20injecting%20funds%20into%20a%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-warner-bros-netflix-paramount-do-whats-right-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweighing%20in%20on%20mergers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20implementing%20legally%20questionable%20tariffs%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat.%20Many%20critics%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20risks%20arising%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20actions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20potential%20for%20politically%20biased%20decision-making%2C%20the%20appearance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-crony-capitalism-luigi-zingales-12-2018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrony%20capitalism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20possible%20market%20distortions.%20In%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20these%20maneuvers%20may%20be%20financially%20minor%2C%20but%20they're%20structurally%20major%20developments.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20drawbacks%2C%20it's%20indicative%20of%20where%20we're%20headed.%20There%20may%20be%20no%20going%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20these%20tools%20generally%20only%20goes%20in%20one%20direction%2C%20and%20so%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20has%20introduced%20a%20new%20group%20of%20tools%20into%20the%20economic%20statecraft%20toolkit%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Aaron%20Bartnick%2C%20a%20former%20White%20House%20economic%20security%20official%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%20and%20a%20current%20fellow%20at%20Columbia%20University.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20administration%20comes%20next%2C%20whether%20Republican%20or%20Democrat%2C%20will%20find%20it%20very%20tempting%20to%20continue%20to%20use%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hasn't%20all%20happened%20out%20of%20nowhere%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US%20has%2C%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20been%20increasingly%20comf