%20to%20the%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20overall%2C%20the%20US%20has%20largely%20taken%20a%20hands-off%20approach%20to%20the%20economy%20over%20the%20last%2040%20years%20and%20been%20critical%20of%20countries%20that%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20has%20spent%20decades%20tsk-tsking%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20about%20state-owned%20enterprises%20and%20industrial%20policy%20and%20state%20capitalism%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Scott%20Lincicome%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20general%20economics%20and%20trade%20at%20the%20Cato%20Institute%2C%20a%20libertarian%20think%20tank.%20On%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20current%20about-face%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hypocrisy%20is%20pretty%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETell%20us%20what%20you%20think%20about%20the%20Future%20of%20Capitalism%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-your-views-on-capitalism-survey-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etaking%20our%20survey%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20turn%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20further.%20Instead%20of%20deploying%20a%20more%20typical%20playbook%20%E2%80%94%20grants%2C%20loans%2C%20tariffs%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20at%20least%20somewhat%20neutral%20in%20its%20application%2C%20the%20White%20House%20is%20now%20picking%20and%20choosing%20companies%20to%20get%20involved%20in.%20In%20broad%20strokes%2C%20one%20can%20see%20what%20they're%20getting%20at%20here.%20The%20companies%20on%20Trump's%20investment%20list%20are%20in%20important%20sectors%20where%20the%20US%20lags%20behind%2C%20and%20they%20fit%20into%20the%20president's%20overall%20theory%20of%20the%20case%20on%20the%20economy%3A%20it's%20better%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-masculine-many-manufacturing-jobs-factories-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C