0student%20understanding.%3Cp%3Ewhitebalance.space%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20NYU%20professor%20turned%20to%20AI%20oral%20exams%20after%20student%20work%20began%20resembling%20McKinsey%20memos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20used%20an%20AI%20agent%20to%20scale%20oral%20exams%2C%20a%20format%20long%20viewed%20as%20too%20time-consuming%20to%20run.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20experiment%20comes%20as%20universities%20reassess%20how%20to%20test%20students%20fairly%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assignments%20looked%20brilliant.%20The%20understanding%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20an%20NYU%20business%20school%20professor%20decided%20to%20fight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-student-ai-changed-study-habits-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-assisted%20coursework%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20AI-powered%20oral%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPanos%20Ipeirotis%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20NYU's%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business%20who%20teaches%20data%20science%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20last%20week%20that%20he%20became%20concerned%20about%20student%20assignments%20that%20read%20like%20%26quot%3Ba%20McKinsey%20memo%26quot%3B%20but%20lacked%20genuine%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20called%20on%20students%20in%20class%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20defend%20their%20submissions%2C%20many%20struggled%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cannot%20defend%20your%20own%20work%20live%2C%20then%20the%20written%20artifact%20is%20not%20measuring%20what%20you%20think%20it%20is%20measuring%2C%26quot%3B%20Ipeirotis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d4acdbc-706e-4774-9c8e-2ad8d7dead75%5C%22%3E'Fight%20fire%20with%20fire'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20that%2C%20he%20revived%20oral%20exams%20and%20enlisted%20an%20AI%20agent%20to%20administer%20them%20at%20scale%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20fire%20with%20fire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20assessments%20that%20evolve%20toward%20formats%20that%20reward%20understanding%2C%20decision-making%2C%20and%20real-time%20reasoning%2C%26quot%3B%20Ipeirotis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOral%20exams%20used%20to%20be%20standard%20until%20they%20could%20not%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20AI%20is%20making%20them%20scalable%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20blog%20post%20detailing%20the%20experiment%2C%20Ipeirotis%20said%20he%20and%20his%20colleague%20built%20the%20AI%20examiner%20using%20ElevenLabs'%20conversational%20speech%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20write%20a%20prompt%20describing%20what%20the%20agent%20should%20ask%20the%20student%2C%20and%20you%20are%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20took%20minutes%20to%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oral%20exam%20had%20two%20parts.%20First%2C%20the%20AI%20agent%20questioned%20students%20about%20their%20capstone%20projects%2C%20probing%20their%20decisions%20and%20reasoning.%20Then%20it%20selected%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20discussed%20in%20class%20and%20pushed%20students%20to%20think%20through%20it%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20nine%20days%2C%20the%20system%20assessed%2036%20students.%20Each%20session%20lasted%20about%2025%20minutes%2C%20with%20total%20compute%20costs%20coming%20in%20at%20about%20%2415%20for%20all%2036%20students.%20A%20human-run%20oral%20exam%20could%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20at%20teaching-assistant%20rates%2C%20Ipeirotis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIpeirotis%20also%20used%20AI%20to%20grade%20the%20exams.%20Three%20AI%20models%20%E2%80%94%20Claude%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20independently%20assessed%20each%20transcript.%20They%20then%20reviewed%20one%20another's%20evaluations%2C%20revised%20their%20scores%2C%20and%20produced%20a%20final%20grade%2C%20with%20Claude%20acting%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bchair%26quot%3B%20to%20synthesize%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIpeirotis%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcouncil%20of%20LLMs%26quot%3B%20graded%20more%20consistently%20than%20humans%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bmore%20strictly%2C%20but%20more%20fairly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20feedback%20was%20better%20than%20any%20human%20would%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20AI%20analysis%20also%20surfaced%20gaps%20in%20how%20the%20material%20had%20been%20taught.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-students-use-ai-homework-study-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudents%20were%20divided%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Only%20a%20small%20minority%20preferred%20the%20AI%20oral%20exams%2C%20and%20many%20found%20them%20more%20stressful%20than%20written%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20even%20while%20acknowledging%20they%20were%20a%20better%20measure%20of%20real%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Ipeirotis%20said%20the%20oral%20exams%20demonstrated%20%26quot%3Bhow%20learning%20is%20supposed%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20practice%2C%20the%20better%20you%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Ipeirotis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214bc0061-23ab-409b-a865-81f4dc76f3e6%5C%22%3EUsing%20AI%20in%20exams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIpeirotis'%20blog%20post%20comes%20as%20universities%20grapple%20with%20how%20to%20test%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-reveals-how-broken-our-education-system-is-economist-says-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudents%20in%20the%20AI%20era%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20paper%20published%20in%20September%20in%20the%20academic%20journal%20%26quot%3BAssessment%20%26amp%3B%20Evaluation%20in%20Higher%20Education%26quot%3B%20said%20AI%20has%20turned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-college-exams-wicked-problem-no-clear-fix-researchers-warn-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20%26quot%