e%20over%20in%20a%20few%20years.%3Cp%3EFINN%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHuman%20feedback%20remains%20essential%20for%20AI%20training%2C%20says%20Invisible%20Technologies'%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESynthetic%20data%20can't%20replace%20humans%20because%20there%20are%20too%20many%20kinds%20of%20tasks%20for%20AI%20to%20accomplish.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20labeling%20startups%20continue%20to%20hire%20specialized%20workers%20as%20tech%20giants%20seek%20high-quality%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20won't%20be%20training%20AI%20anytime%20soon%2C%20says%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20data%20labeling%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20last%20week%2C%20Matt%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-senior-executive-departing-to-head-new-ai-company-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInvisible%20Technologies%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20misconceptions%20in%20the%20AI%20training%20industry%20is%20that%20humans%20won't%20be%20needed%20in%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20started%20this%20job%2C%20the%20main%20push%20back%20I%20always%20got%20was%20that%20synthetic%20data%20will%20take%20over%20and%20you%20just%20will%20not%20need%20human%20feedback%20two%20to%20three%20years%20from%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20startup%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20first%20principles%2C%20that%20actually%20doesn't%20make%20very%20much%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESynthetic%20data%20refers%20to%20data%20that%20is%20artificially%20created.%20It%20is%20used%20for%20training%20AI%20or%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20mostly%20where%20real%20data%20is%20scarce%20or%20can't%20be%20used%20because%20of%20privacy%20concerns.%20Human%20feedback%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20asks%20real%20people%20to%20